      "body" : "It is true String#matches() matches the entire string by default but <code>&quot;123abc&quot;.matches(&quot;^[0-9]+.*$&quot;)</code> or <code>&quot;123abc&quot;.matches(&quot;[0-9]+.*&quot;)</code>  works too"
