    "answer_id" : 8923449,
    "question_id" : 8923398,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>java's implementation of regexes try to match the whole string</p>\n\n<p>that's different from perl regexes, which try to find a matching part</p>\n\n<p>if you want to find a string with nothing but lower case characters, use the pattern <code>[a-z]+</code></p>\n\n<p>if you want to find a string containing at least one lower case character, use the pattern <code>.*[a-z].*</code></p>\n"
  }, {
